  { heading: 'Diverse Expertise', text: 'I have a rare blend of product design, UX research, and leadership experience across industries, from startups to blue-chip brands.' },
  { heading: 'Tech & Design Fusion', text: 'I combine technical knowledge with high-quality UX and visual design, building responsive digital products with HTML, CSS, Webflow and now Claude Code.' },
  { heading: 'Business Acumen & Critical Thinking', text: 'Founding and managing my own startups and working with several other startups, highlights my end-to-end skills in product concept ideation, design, and execution.' },
  { heading: 'Global Impact', text: 'My career spans multiple countries, industries, and remote roles, reflecting adaptability and global relevance.' },
  { heading: 'Speed & Attention to detail', text: 'I continuously upgrade my wide skillset, and use agentic AI for optimum efficiency.' },
];

const testimonials = [
  { quote: "Rachael has been my secret weapon when it comes to design. Her many years of professional work, her keen aesthetic sense, and her ability to put focus on what's important at the right time have made a tremendous difference. Thanks to Rachael, we have a valuable new app for the business that is a cornerstone to our success. I'm lucky to have found someone who is both in my corner and able to help me express my vision to the world.", name: 'Scott Whittle, Terra CEO', location: 'Cape May, NJ, USA' },
  { quote: "Rachael reworked our existing B2B tool's UX and expanded on it. The services offered are complex and there were many legacy parameters to contend with. Rachael came up with a much improved flow, she is not afraid of questioning the status quo to get the best outcome for the user, and the outcome is a much more user friendly and scalable UX. I would happily employ Rachael again.", name: 'Margaret Sliman, Inivio Manager', location: 'Sydney, AU' },
  { quote: "Rachael is a very professional and capable UX Designer with a strong business and entrepreneurial mindset. When she worked onsite for my client she performed what she was asked to do, to a very high standard, and left the project in a much stronger condition than when she first joined. I can strongly recommend Rachael for any position that requires UI/IA wire-framing etc.", name: 'Matthew Drake, Recruiter', location: 'Sydney, AU' },
